  <title>13.6.3 Controlling Production Counter</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">Controlling Production Counter</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Below is the procedure to control the incremental counter by issuing a start command by sending an external signal (pulse signal).</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><image src="Ch 4 Fig 13.18.png" scale="25.00%" width="481" height="107" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-left:13px;"><text styleclass="Figure E" style="font-size:11pt;">Figure &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER4=13%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt; Counter Control Timing Chart</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-left:13px;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text style="font-weight:bold;">Control Procedure Using USDO1/USDI1</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s)" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Set the machine parameters as follows:</text></li>
    </list>
    <list id="3" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="·" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body bullet" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Body bullet"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">  No. 11033 (Start Condition Confirm – Single) 0: Not Confirmed</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Body bullet"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">  No. 11041 (Start Condition Confirm – Group) 0: Not Confirmed</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Body bullet"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">  No. 11049 (Start Condition Confirm – Single) 0: Not Confirmed</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Body bullet"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">  No. 11057 (Finish Condition Confirm – Group) 0: Not Confirmed</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Body bullet"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">  No. 11073 (Operation Completion Time Limit) 5: 5 [sec]</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Body bullet"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">  No. 11089 (Off Operation Completion Delay Time) 0: 0 [msec]</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Body bullet"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">  No. 11081 (On Operation Completion Delay Time) 10: 1000 [msec]</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Body bullet" style="line-height:1.00;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">  No. 11065 (USDO1 turn off after operation completion) 1: Turned off</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Body bullet" style="margin-top:0px;"></para>
    <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s)" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Connect the counter and the output signal terminal in the machine controller with cables. Connect the counter to USDO1.</text></li>
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Issue M581 in MDI mode to confirm the counter operation. check the operation status and adjust the on completion delay time to the optimum value with machine parameter No. 11081 (USDO1/USDI1 On Operation Delay Time).</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; page-break-before:always;"></para>
  </body>
